creator: ePACT Network Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
Anytime, Anywhere Access to Member Records!

The ePACT Admin App allows authorized users to securely access critical member information day-to-day and in an emergency, including in offline mode. Staff can quickly and easily view medical and contact details, sign members in and out, or send messages direct from their smartphone or tablet.

Critical Information at Your Fingertips: View medical information (including allergies and dietary needs), flagged conditions, medications and treatments, and waivers and consents.

Send General & Emergency Messages: Send email, text, and voice messages to groups, members, and emergency contacts to ensure that no one misses out on important information.

Check Members In and Out: Eliminate paper sign in/out forms, improve the drop-off and pick-up process for families, and automatically archive records for licensing requirements.
descriptionShort: Secure access to your members’ critical data no matter where you are!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Added Absent status and Batch Check In, Check Out features
- New UI design
- Bug fixes
